snippet.title: Диана открывает календарь Барби Diana Opens Advent Calendar with Barbie doll surprise for kids
snippet.description:
Diana Opens Advent Calendar with Barbie and surprise for doll. Includes Barbie doll and advent calendar with clothing and accessories for five different careers.
This Barbie doll advent calendar will inspire all year long with 24 days of gifts -- with Barbie doll by 23 career-themed clothing items and accessories! Diana will open all the surprises for the Barbie doll immediately.

Диана открывает Адвент календарь з Барби и с Одеждой для пяти разных профессий куклы Барби
